snippet.title: INSTANT Chef Party - The Cooking Show Must Go On! Trailer (EN)
snippet.description:
No cooking skills are required... except, maybe, for toasting marshmallows!

INSTANT Chef Party is a party game planned exclusively on Nintendo Switch this fall !

More information : https://www.justforgames.com/product/instant-chef-party/
